# --- Node / build artifacts (must NOT poison the build context) ---
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/coverage

# --- Env files: never bake secrets into an image layer ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# --- VCS / editor / OS cruft ---
.git
.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# --- Docker / infra meta (not needed inside the frontend image) ---
docker-compose*.yml
**/Dockerfile*
README.md
DEPLOYMENT.md
nginx/
certbot/
